OOC:  I dont know Zardus, i was desperate for a name

:::Sharpedge/Jetstorm/Starscream/Airazor/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky Lynx/Torca:::

::Sharpedge is amazed.  Deemos put him in the lead!::
Sharpedge: Alright guys.  We are about to enggae the enemy.  I say that we 
divide up the atacks between all of us and then the Mafia forms Mobster.  We 
take no prisoners, except maybe the pod.  Ready? Lets go!
::He marhces out, Jetstorm following him::
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
Starscream: Right.
::He transforms to jet mode::
Starscream: Hop on.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
::All of my Maximals head to the battle.  Torca sees Klant.::
Torca: Defeinatly, were partners!  lets get out of here and get to the battle!


--part1_b8.ef31966.2767888e_boundary
